Enjoy the most fun and addictive BTS-2048 puzzle game now!
Play Jimin, jin. jungkook, suga, jhope and taehyung card play with your friends
select 4x4 6x6 and 8x8 2048 puzzle game.
Feel the amazingly smooth and comfortable controls you will just love :)
Get to the BTS-2048 tile with the least moves possible and post your scores to the leaderboard!


HOW TO PLAY:
Add up the same numbers until you get to the BTS-2048 tile!
Once you achieve your goal to BTS-2048, you can go on to the next level, 4096 & 8192!!!
Just swipe the tiles to move up and down, left and right.

You must sign in using google account to access the Leaderboard, so please make fure you have installed google+ on your phone or tablet.

FEATURES:
- 4 languages supported so far (Chinese, Vietnamese, French & English)
- Clear and simple UI
- Supports BGM
- Supports swipe sounds
- Supports animation speed controls
- Supports Undo options
- High score
- Leaderboard
- Supports all Android devices including tablets.


