BTS-Jungkook Jump
About this game
Tap, tap, tap ... jump, jump, jump. Jump from one tree to the other, defeat enemies in your way. Climb as high as you can while avoiding squirrels, birds, snakes, monkeys and more impediments. Hit three same consecutive enemies to get a bonus power-up skill. Grab shields for protection.

GAME FEATURES
● Amazing power-up skills!
● More enemies and impediments
● Endless ninja
